                                                               |u, u, d>, |u, u, u>]

 -- Function: complete (B)
     The function ‘complete’ generates the completeness relation for the
     basis set ‘B’.

     (%i1) B:basis_set(1,[0,1]);
     (%o1)                             [|1>, |0>]
     (%i2) complete(B);
     (%o2)                        |1> . <1| + |0> . <0|

